-- Avoca Capital Hires Freeman’s Hatchley as Co-Chief Executive
-- B y   P a t r i c i a   K u o
-- 2012-05-29T09:45:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-29/avoca-capital-hires-freeman-s-hatchley-as-co-chief-executive.html
Avoca Capital Holdings,  a credit
manager overseeing 6 billion euros ($7.5 billion) of assets,
hired James Hatchley as co-chief executive officer.  Hatchley joins from financial advisory firm Freeman & Co.
where he was a managing director, Dublin-based Avoca said in a
statement today. Hatchley, who will be based in Dublin and
 London , will work alongside Chief Executive Officer Alan Burke
and Chairman Donal Daly.  “Further growth opportunities are expected to arise as a
result of the continuing restructuring of the European banking
and credit markets,” Avoca said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Kuo in London at 
